---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Metromedics SAS | Calibración y Mantenimiento de Equipos Médicos e Industriales"
  description="Metromedics S.A.S Dosquebradas: Expertos en Calibración y Mantenimiento de Equipos Médicos e Industriales. Contribuimos a la Estandarización de la Medición en el Sector de la Salud y la Industria."
>
  <!-- Modern Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-medical-blue to-primary-600 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-display-lg font-bold mb-6">Laboratorio Acreditado ONAC</h1>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
          Certificado bajo la norma ISO/IEC 17025:2017 con código de acreditación 18-LAC-020.
          Garantizamos la máxima precisión y trazabilidad en nuestros servicios de calibración.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contacto" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white text-medical-blue font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            Solicitar Calibración
          </a>
          <a href="#magnitudes" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-semibold rounded-xl border-2 border-white/30 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
            </svg>
            Ver Magnitudes
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ONAC Certification Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-large p-8 mb-12">
          <img src="/images/onac_grande.png" alt="Certificación ONAC MetroMedics" class="mx-auto mb-6 max-h-32" />
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Acreditación ONAC Vigente</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            En MetroMedics SAS contamos con acreditación ONAC vigente a la fecha, con
            <strong class="text-medical-blue">código de acreditación 18-LAC-020</strong>,
            bajo la norma ISO/IEC 17025: 2017. Esta certificación garantiza la competencia
            técnica y confiabilidad de nuestros servicios de calibración.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Magnitudes Section -->
  <section id="magnitudes" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-display-md font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Magnitudes <span class="text-medical-blue">Acreditadas</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Ofrecemos servicios de calibración acreditados en las siguientes magnitudes,
          con los más altos estándares de precisión y trazabilidad.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Magnitud Masa -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-large overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-square relative overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/item2-291x300.jpg"
              alt="Calibración de Magnitud Masa"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16l3-1m-3 1l-3-1"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Magnitud Masa</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Instrumentos de pesaje no automático: <strong>1 mg ≤ m ≤ 1000 kg</strong></span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Pesas clase OIML M1, M2, M3: <strong>1 g a 20 kg</strong></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Magnitud Presión -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-large overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-square relative overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/item1-292x300.jpg"
              alt="Calibración de Magnitud Presión"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Magnitud Presión</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Tensiómetros: <strong>50mmHg a 300mmHg / 6.67 KPa a 40 KPa</strong></span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Vacuómetros, manómetros, manovacuómetros: <strong>-10 a 1500 psi</strong></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Temperatura y Humedad Relativa -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-large overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-square relative overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/items_temp_relativa-292x300.jpg"
              alt="Calibración de Temperatura y Humedad Relativa"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Temperatura y Humedad</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Temperatura ambiente: <strong>10 °C a 40 °C</strong></span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Humedad relativa: <strong>15%HR a 90%HR</strong></span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Termohigrómetros, higrómetros, termómetros digitales, sensores, dataloggers</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Temperatura de Contacto -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-large overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-square relative overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/items_temp-292x300.jpg"
              alt="Calibración de Temperatura de Contacto"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Temperatura de Contacto</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Alcance acreditado: <strong>-30 °C a 350 °C</strong></span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Termómetros de cadena de frío, termómetros de punzón, sensores de temperatura, termoresistores, dataloggers de alta temperatura, controladores</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Caracterización de Equipos -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-large overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 lg:col-span-2 xl:col-span-1">
          <div class="aspect-square relative overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/isotermicos3.png"
              alt="Caracterización de Equipos Isotérmicos"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Caracterización de Equipos</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Temperatura: <strong>-30 °C a 350 °C</strong></span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-medical-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Humedad relativa: <strong>30%HR a 85%HR</strong></span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Cámaras ambientales, hornos, incubadoras, refrigeradores, congeladores, bloques secos</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-medical-blue to-primary-600 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">¿Necesitas calibración acreditada para tus equipos?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8">
          Confía en nuestro laboratorio acreditado ONAC para garantizar la precisión
          y trazabilidad de tus instrumentos de medición.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contacto"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-medical-blue font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors shadow-lg"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
            </svg>
            Solicitar Cotización
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:+5760635261611"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-semibold rounded-xl border-2 border-white/30 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
            </svg>
            Llamar Ahora
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
